This directory contains the unmodified `mz80' (`Multi-Z80 CPU
emulator') sources, version 2.6, taken from

	ftp://ftp.synthcom.com/pub/emulators/cpu/makez80.zip

`mz80' is copr. Neil Bradley (neil@synthcom.com); see `mz80.txt' for
details on copyright and license. `mz80' is distributed in unmodified
form in accordance with its licensing conditions.

This directory also contains a patch `makez80.c.dif', which is
required to make `mz80' work with `mz800em', and a `Makefile'. Both
are copr. Matthias K"oppe (mkoeppe@mail.math.uni-magdeburg.de).
